title: Poker Bible Funny
description:
Titanpoker.com's Poker Bible is a humorist book made up for poker fans connecting both the world of the bible and its scripts and that of the poker game. There is no intention here to hurt the feelings of believers of any religion and if by any chance is anybody hurt by this collection, please accept in advance our apologies. In the process of the work we have included also illustrations thanks to Sweet Publishing
See the whole project at http://www.titanpoker.com/bible.html.
